Contained in this archive are several pieces of source which represents a small
section of the half-hearted and unfinished projects I have done. It also
represents the fact that I have terrible problem when it comes to programming in
that I lose motivation. :) Anyway I won't say that these programs are examples
of good coding or good coding practices but they worked, on my machine at least.
Most programs have a little readme at the start of the source which gives you a
little bit of information about it. I'm also lazy and don't comment a lot of the
source, so you're on your own there. Anyway, you are free to use this source
code in any of your own projects, anyway you see fit, at your own risk of course
:)

IMPORTANT
---------

Many of the examples use certain fonts so copy the supplied fonts to your fonts
directory. Same applies to the libraries, copy them to libs. There are some
modules included which you may need ,to recompile some of the examples. Copy
them to the appropriate place in EMODULES:
-Read the start of the source before compiling or running
-I also recommend you run most of the programmings from the CLI, after CD-ing to
-the directory in which they are contained.


