civ2.e
An attempt at a multiplayer battle-game. Development lost momentum completely.
This was really going to be for a graphics card. I must say that not all the
graphics and sound files were done by me, but many of them were. The mod files
used was certainly not going to be the final choice but was included to test the
mod routine.

